JENNIFER GOVE: Great.

00:00:04.010 --> 00:00:05.440
Such a wonderful crowd.

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:08.960
Thank you so much for all
coming to my talk today.

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:13.420
So my name is Jenny Gove and
I'm a User Experience Researcher

00:00:13.420 --> 00:00:14.690
here at Google.

00:00:14.690 --> 00:00:17.960
I've been at Google, now,
this month, for 10 years,

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:19.590
and I heard that
that coincides--

00:00:19.590 --> 00:00:20.090
[CLAPPING]

00:00:20.090 --> 00:00:20.833
Thank you.

